@startuml runtime-sequence-gate-evaluation-decision-path-v1
title Gate Evaluation Decision Path (Application Runtime)

participant "LangGraph Orchestrator\nAPP-016" as APP_016
participant "PM Agent\nAPP-007" as APP_007
participant "Specialist Agent\nAPP-008" as APP_008
participant "CSCO Agent\nAPP-015" as APP_015
participant "EngagementSession\nAPP-017" as APP_017
database "EventStore\nAPP-001" as APP_001

APP_016 -> APP_007: evaluate_gate_readiness(gate_id, phase_id, context_ref)
loop for each required reviewer input
  APP_007 -> APP_008: provide_reviewer_recommendation(gate_id)
  APP_016 -> APP_015: request_safety_vote(gate_id, context_ref)
  APP_015 --> APP_007: return_safety_vote(vote, rationale)
end
APP_007 -> APP_001: append_event(event_type="gate.evaluated", gate_id, decision)

alt gate passed with CSCO vote present
  APP_016 -> APP_001: append_event(event_type="phase.transitioned", gate_id, to_phase_id)
  APP_016 -> APP_001: create_snapshot(trigger="gate.evaluated")
  APP_016 -> APP_017: start_next_phase_iteration(to_phase_id)
  APP_017 -> APP_001: append_event(event_type="sprint.started", sprint_id) [if new sprint]
else CSCO vote missing/timeout or gate failed/deferred
  APP_016 -> APP_001: append_event(event_type="algedonic.escalated", reason="gate-safety-vote-timeout", gate_id)
  APP_016 -> APP_001: append_event(event_type="decision.recorded", decision="rework-required", gate_id)
  APP_016 -> APP_008: dispatch_rework_package(target_specialist_id, rework_scope)
  APP_016 -> APP_017: retain_current_phase_and_track_rework(gate_id)
end

note right of APP_007
Mapped to BPR-004 gate evaluation and
PM tool contract evaluate_gate().
Reviewer roster is phase/gate-policy dependent;
CSCO is mandatory for safety/governance checks.
Safety default is fail-closed when CSCO safety vote is unavailable.
end note
@enduml
